ef=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概要","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><br>\n <strong>HTML <code>&lt;object&gt;</code> 元素</strong>（或者称作 <em>HTML 嵌入对象元素</em>）表示引入一个外部资源，这个资源可能是一张图片，一个嵌入的浏览上下文，亦或是一个插件所使用的资源。<p></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/object.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">内容分类</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Flow content</a>; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">phrasing content</a>; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#embedded_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Embedded content\">embedded content</a>, palpable content; if the element has a <strong>usemap</strong> attribute, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#interactive_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Interactive content\">interactive content</a>; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#form_listed\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Form listed\">listed</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#form_submittable\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Form submittable\">submittable</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#form-associated_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Form-associated content\">form-associated</a> element.</li>\n <li><dfn>允许内容</dfn> zero or more <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/param\"><code>&lt;param&gt;</code></a> elements, then <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#transparent_content_models\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Transparent content models\">Transparent content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>标签闭合</dfn> 不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</li>\n <li><dfn>允许的父级元素</dfn> Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#embedded_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Embedded content\">embedded content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>DOM 接口</dfn> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLObjectElement\"><code>HTMLObjectElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>元素包含<a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">全局属性</a>。</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"archive\"><a id=\"attr-archive\" href=\"#attr-archive\"><b><code>archive</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>用来指名对象资源列表的以空格分隔的 URI 列表。</dd>\n <dt id=\"border\"><a id=\"attr-border\" href=\"#attr-border\"><b><code>border</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>元素周围的边框的宽度，单位为像素。</dd>\n <dt id=\"classid\"><a id=\"attr-classid\" href=\"#attr-classid\"><b><code>classid</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>对象实现的 URI，可以同时与 <strong>data</strong> 属性使用，或者使用 <strong>data</strong> 属性替代。</dd>\n <dt id=\"codebase\"><a id=\"attr-codebase\" href=\"#attr-codebase\"><b><code>codebase</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>解析 <strong>classid</strong>，<strong>data</strong> 或者 <strong>archive</strong> 中定义的相对路径的根路径，如果没有定义，默认为当前文档的 base URI。</dd>\n <dt id=\"codetype\"><a id=\"attr-codetype\" href=\"#attr-codetype\"><b><code>codetype</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd><strong>classid</strong> 定义的 data 的内容类型。</dd>\n <dt id=\"data\"><a id=\"attr-data\" href=\"#attr-data\"><b><code>data</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>一个合法的 URL 作为资源的地址，，需要为 <strong>data</strong> 和 <strong>type </strong>中至少一个设置值。</dd>\n <dt id=\"declare\"><a id=\"attr-declare\" href=\"#attr-declare\"><b><code>declare</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>取值为布尔的属性可以设置这个元素为仅声明的格式。对象必须被随后的 <code>&lt;object&gt; 元素实例化。在</code> HTML5 中，完整的重复 &lt;object&gt; 元素，可以重用元素。</dd>\n <dt id=\"form\"><a id=\"attr-form\" href=\"#attr-form\"><b><code>form</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>对象元素关联的 form 元素（属于的 form）。取值必须是同一文档下的一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> 元素的 ID。</dd>\n <dt id=\"height\"><a id=\"attr-height\" href=\"#attr-height\"><b><code>height</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>资源显示的高度，单位是 CSS 像素。</dd>\n <dt id=\"name\"><a id=\"attr-name\" href=\"#attr-name\"><b><code>name</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>浏览上下文名称（HTML5），或者控件名称（HTML 4）。</dd>\n <dt id=\"standby\"><a id=\"attr-standby\" href=\"#attr-standby\"><b><code>standby</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>对象的实现和数据加载过程中，浏览器可以显示的信息。</dd>\n <dt id=\"tabindex\"><a id=\"attr-tabindex\" href=\"#attr-tabindex\"><b><code>tabindex</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>当前元素在文档 Tab 导航中的顺序。</dd>\n <dt id=\"type\"><a id=\"attr-type\" href=\"#attr-type\"><b><code>type</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd><strong>data</strong> 指定的资源的 MIME 类型，需要为 <strong>data</strong> 和 <strong>type </strong>中至少一个设置值。</dd>\n <dt id=\"usemap\"><a id=\"attr-usemap\" href=\"#attr-usemap\"><b><code>usemap</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>指向一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a> 元素的 hash-name；格式为 ‘#’ 加 map 元素 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map#attr-name\"><code>name</code></a> 元素的值。</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\"><a id=\"attr-width\" href=\"#attr-width\"><b><code>width</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>资源显示的宽度，单位是 CSS 像素。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Embed a flash movie --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>object</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>move.swf<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>application/x-shockwave-flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Embed a flash movie with parameters --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>object</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>move.swf<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>application/x-shockwave-flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>param</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>foo<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/the-iframe-element.html#the-object-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;object&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/the-object-element.html#the-object-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;object&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/objects.html#h-13.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">&lt;object&gt;</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.object","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参阅","title":"参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/applet\"><code>&lt;applet&gt;</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/param\"><code>&lt;param&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"specifications"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参阅","id":"参阅"}],"summary":"元素包含全局属性。","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<object>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<object>: The External Object element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<object>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<object>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<object>: 外部オブジェクト要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<object>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/object","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/object/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object","title":"<object>"}],"pageTitle":"<object> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}